text.id: Explore community assets created by artists.
text.tspan: Explore community assets created by artists.

text.id: SSX is a community-building research & creation project using Extended Reality (XR) (ie. Virtual, Augmented, Mixed Realities) to foster new works by artists from the Asian diaspora. Sari-Sari Xchange Assetory (SSXA) is a virtual asset library created with and for the Asian diaspora community.
